<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Paradox_of_hedonism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Aristotle, <i><a href="/wiki/Nicomachean_Ethics" title="Nicomachean Ethics">Nicomachean Ethics</a></i> 1175, 3-6 in <i>The Basic Works of Aristotle</i>, <a href="/wiki/Richard_McKeon" title="Richard McKeon">Richard McKeon</a> ed. (New York: Random House, 1941)</li>
<li>John Stuart Mill, <i>Autobiography</i> in <i>The Harvard Classics</i>, Vol. 25, Charles Eliot Norton, ed. (New York: P. F. Collier &amp; Son Company, 1909)</li>
